             depos'd, That he going his Rounds found the Prosecutor's back Door open, the Window down, and the Good, saying very oddly about the House, and two Pillow Cases fill'd with Goods, as pack'd up to carry away; that this Deponent went up to the Room where 
               <persName id="t17280117-40-person204">
                  William 
                  Mathews 
               <interp inst="t17280117-40-person204" type="surname" value="Mathews"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17280117-40-person204" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17280117-40-person204" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             lay, and ask'd him if he was not Accessory to what was done; and upon the Prosecutor's coming and charging him, he confess'd he did believe his Brother had done it, saying, he had agreed with his Brother to rob his Master's House, but was no ways Assistance in this Action.</p>
